{"tid":440935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★10-19 集體投訴：iOS 11 是史上最多 bug 的 iOS！","createTime":"2017-10-19T08:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T11:36:12.000Z","uid":19454,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a38d2bad18eecf57ca29927330c7a3920da09adc","tid":440935,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:23:58.000Z","msg":"有網民 rainbowcornrows 在 Reddit 討論區大吐苦水，直指 iOS 11 「史上最 bug」，「bug」的程度可以令他改用 Android，他投訴這升級 iOS 11 後問題出現得太頻繁，例如在聽電話的時候突然無法對話，甚至重新開機才能解決，又例如打電話的時候沒有撥號聲、就算調整音量，音量介面也沒有顯示出來，令他每次打電話都要重新啟動。除此之外，他發現在聽音樂的時候音樂介面不會在鎖定介面出現，而且音量不能調整，更甚的是 iPhone 經常停頓不能運作，每次也是重新啟動才能解決。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/10/ios-11-is-the-buggest_02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F10%2Fios-11-is-the-buggest_02.png&h=8dfe4821&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上述這口苦水引來超過 1700 個網民回應，他們的 iOS 11 裝置同樣有大量問題出現。其中網民 Dr_Ghamorra 回應指升級 iOS 11 後變得一團糟，鍵盤不能關閉，只能重新開啟訊息 App 解決，螢幕會突然變成橫置而且不能回復原狀、而且在 4 小時之內突然用了 500MB 數據，電池消耗太厲害，在戶外他連輸入文字也不敢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/10/19/ios-11-is-the-buggest/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F10%2F19%2Fios-11-is-the-buggest%2F&d=awM1WCYJ6JNa6LRpoiqvWrZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=59a9a7a2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/10/19/ios-11-is-the-buggest/</a>"},{"pid":"2da5f3aa6583c34b63a06da58bb8e6eba591cb70","tid":440935,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:24:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b8461f1ec59287bd703e1521a39556e99f3c107","